org.bukkit

Interface World.ChunkLoadCallback

  • Enclosing interface:
    World

    public static interface World.ChunkLoadCallback
    Used by World.getChunkAtAsync(Location,ChunkLoadCallback) methods to request a Chunk to be loaded, with this callback receiving the chunk when it is finished. This callback will be executed on synchronously on the main thread. Timing and order this callback is fired is intentionally not defined and and subject to change.
